{"tid":296113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［又有後生跳樓]19歲青年長青邨墮樓亡","createTime":"2017-06-24T10:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T10:55:26.000Z","uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffc6395fad0e53665b7bb74eaee7599278e52882","tid":296113,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:20:02.000Z","msg":"【15：26更新】新增影片<br />\n早上11時許，一名年約20歲青年，被發現倒卧在青衣長青邨青楊樓對開天井，重傷昏迷，救護員接報到場，證實男事主當場死亡，一名女親友聞訊趕到認屍，其間表現傷心，坐在不遠的休憩處長凳上，一度攬著女警抱頭痛哭，其後另一名較年輕的女親友亦趕至，兩女擁抱傷心落淚。警方調查後，證實男事主姓曾（19歲），由上址走廊墮下，據悉，事主有情緒病。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56870031&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56870031%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170624&d=D2gOzWXn%2FtUZh2njCm6n9J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=704669d3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56870031%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170624&h=999a2b8d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56870031&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170624</a>"},{"pid":"c507135c52e71cbf734d6c7822d2cd3e1c959504","tid":296113,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾90後唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1783a613287fee4af209ef18164469a56424c2f8","tid":296113,"uid":8922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"巴打rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n準備跳樓，你問我答<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/295497/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/295497/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"151d6b1ec6e5c0154494bb4ca63216c14d69b3bd","tid":296113,"uid":62822,"